oai_dc:dc.dc:description: 0.15 Cubic feet 1 box The James King Ashley Civil War manuscript (undated; 0.15 cubic feet; 1 box) comprises a handwritten memoir written by James King Ashley of the 20th Indiana Battery, recounting his experiences during the Civil War.
